                        <interp inst="t18400511-name-114" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS KERSWELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I heard the cry of "Stop thief"—I saw the pri<lb></lb>soner running, caught him in Russell-square, and brought him back.</p>
